Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:15.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣き出しそうな顔で憂う低い空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:15.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴沉低空下你一脸仿佛要哭出来的忧郁表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:20.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苛立ち混じりの唾を吐く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:20.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混杂焦虑的抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:28.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが壊れそうな不安抱いて明日に怯え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:28.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕破碎而恐惧明天来临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明後日ばっか見てたって答えは出ないことだって分かって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里明白就算一味期待后天也无法找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:38.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限りなく広がる真っ白な
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:38.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若前途无限光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:42.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:42.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们还能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実が染ゆく真っ暗な
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:51.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若现实早已被黑暗所染
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:56.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:56.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们又能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もがき輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有以抗争展现光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近街上多了很多黄色的人诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说黄巾贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谣言说砍人魔是DOLLARS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我们没有你的话就……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近他怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时不时会来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久还刚来过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得东京的空气很浑浊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛔虫 蛔虫 蛔虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限りなく広がる真っ白な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若前途无限光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:31.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:31.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们还能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実が染ゆく真っ暗な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若现实早已被黑暗所染
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:44.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日に何を描く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:44.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们又能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:49.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もがき輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:49.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有以抗争展现光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说刚刚有来良学园的学生被砍人魔袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是乱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如假包换
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是袭击了一年级的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打个电话 先潜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}ROM是Read Only Member的省略型 意思是『只看别人留言自己不发言的人』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似不是你的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道事件发生在哪一带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在首都高速沿线地铁的东池袋站不远处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那附近聚集着很多巡逻车我想很容易认出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 我要下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛顿你要去凑热闹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}赛顿退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话打通了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是现在在警察那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是现场目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}田中太郎退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}甘乐退出聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}现在聊天室里无人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}罪歌进入聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}我砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}想要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}人类 强大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}问谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}谁? 强大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}期望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起这系列血腥事件的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟与一个少女的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我的过去有着紧密的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的我对此还浑然未知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}想要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}物情骚然:是指世间很多骚乱 很不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
